      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i’ve just become a ghost. it’s been months since i could even pick up a brush without feeling nothing. it’s like the part of me that actually lived, the part that saw color and meaning, is just... gone. i'm just sitting here in this skin, but there's nothing inside anymore. just a hollow shell.",
